{"tid":1893980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傻鳩廢中年漢大埔行山昏迷　直升機送院不治","createTime":"2020-02-23T15:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T04:46:27.000Z","uid":236891,"like":49,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"cf94f92489d5230484ccbff8221a9de13fd88230","tid":1893980,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200223/mobile/bkn-20200223210606904-0223_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200223%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200223210606904-0223_00822_001.html&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAykcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=9febea99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200223/mobile/bkn-20200223210606904-0223_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今晚(23日)8時許，一名年約50多歲的姓黃男子偕3名友人於大埔涌背行山，期間突然感到不適，並且陷入昏迷，友人叫喚全無反應，大驚報警求助。救援人員接報登山拯救，政府飛行服務隊直升機亦奉召到場協助，經一番搜索後，鎖定事主位置，稍後將他救起並急送到東區醫院搶救，惜終告不治，警方正進一步調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n諗住避人群病毒上山行吓又不自量力行到死鳩埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n口德值-50"},{"pid":"9d81043665d7424cad48bea14228285686451f69","tid":1893980,"uid":134226,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:27:02.000Z","msg":"添煩添亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e02f542509c312357c6a3aafbe1b773e252c9d1","tid":1893980,"uid":88743,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:28:02.000Z","msg":"係咪佢個武肺功能頂唔住死撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69472818d297a76ac0e52879183fe9a5cb2ff2e9","tid":1893980,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"07b067abe18ba834059a77126cd7b06bfef27e9f","tid":1893980,"uid":88982,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"藍屍+1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76bfc